\"font-size:22px;margin:10px 0;\"><strong>Get 2 Months for the Price of 1</strong></p>\n    <p style=\"color:#fff;\">Use code: <strong>COMEBACK50</strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin-top:15px;\">Limited to the first 50 people who use this code</p>\n  </div>\n  \n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://evofitmeals.com/pricing?code=COMEBACK50\" \n       style=\"background:#FF5722;color:white;padding:15px 30px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;display:inline-block;font-size:18px;\">\n      Claim Your Welcome Back Offer\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  \n  <h3 style=\"margin-top:40px;\">üìÖ Join Our Free Webinar This Week:</h3>\n  <p><strong>\"3 Secrets to Client Compliance: How to Get Clients to Actually Follow Their Meal Plans\"</strong></p>\n  <p>Thursday at 8pm ET - Limited spots available</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://evofitmeals.com/webinar\" \n       style=\"background:#2196F3;color:white;padding:12px 24px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;display:inline-block;\">\n      Save My Seat (Free)\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  \n  <p style=\"margin-top:40px;color:#666;\">\n    Not ready yet? No problem! We'll keep sending you valuable tips and updates each month. \n    Reply to this email with any questions - we're here to help.\n  </p>\n  \n  <p>To your success,<br>The EvoFitMeals Team</p>\n  \n  <p style=\"margin-top:30px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #ccc;color:#999;font-size:12px;\">\n    P.S. The COMEBACK50 code is limited to the first 50 people. If you want to take advantage of this offer, \n    don't wait - it won't last long!\n  </p>\n`;\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    ...($json),\n    subject: subject,\n    htmlContent: htmlContent\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "build-email-content",
      "name": "Build Re-engagement Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [850, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "=https://api.mailgun.net/v3/evofitmeals.com/messages",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "formUrlEncoded",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "from",
              "value": "=EvoFit Meals <invites@evofitmeals.com>"
            },
            {
              "name": "to",
              "value": "={{ $json.email }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "subject",
              "value": "={{ $json.subject }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "html",
              "value": "={{ $json.htmlContent }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "o:tracking",
              "value": "yes"
            },
            {
              "name": "o:tracking-clicks",
              "value": "yes"
            },
            {
              "name": "o:tracking-opens",
              "value": "yes"
            }
          ]
